data.description: From whitewashed brick exterior to exquisite updates to a spacious backyard, this home is truly top-notch. The remodeled kitchen is a showstopper, featuring custom cabinetry and high-end appliances. Enormous dining room will comfortably serve all your friends and family. Designer touches are the perfect accents throughout the home, with updated light fixtures, board and batten, plantation shutters. You'll love the convenience of the primary bedroom on main level with renovated bathroom and spacious closet. The dressing room provides an amazing, unexpected space for pampering yourself with tons of thoughtful storage. Upstairs you'll find 3 generously sized bedrooms and a beautifully remodeled bathroom. Basement is the perfect bonus space with walkout to backyard. This backyard is made for quiet evenings around the built-in fire pit. At night, enjoy custom lighting built into patio seating wall. Home sits on an impressive .79 acre lot, with fully fenced backyard and workshop with power.
